gpx2wkt - converts from GPX to Well-known Text
==============================================

Building:
----------

First you need to get:

* an OCaml compiler >= 3.11 (http://caml.inria.fr/ocaml);
* GNU Make (http://www.gnu.org/software/make/);
* findlib for ocamlfind command
  (http://projects.camlcity.org/projects/findlib.html);
* extlib for OCaml (http://code.google.com/p/ocaml-extlib/);
* xmlm for OCaml (http://erratique.ch/software/xmlm);

Then simply run

> make

Installation:
--------------

> sudo make install

Usage:
-------

> gpx2wkt < /path/to/file.gpx
